For a desired route, find its route id by hand
For a desired stop, find its stop id by hand

For the above given route ids, find all associated trip ids
For trip ids found, get their associated stop times
For stop times found, filter by stop ids found

For each route, find the stop time that is closest to the current time
Format time difference in minutes

Example:

MILLBRAE     1,10 MIN
6-CAR, 2-DOOR